        <heading>Section </heading>
        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 5.  THIRD POSSESSORS
Art. 3315.  Third possessor defined
A third possessor is one who acquires mortgaged property and who is not personally bound for the obligation the mortgage secures.</p>
        </content>
